        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After asking for the doctor’s name, always ask the user for the start date and time of the appointment.
Use the provided value as StartDateTime.
Always calculate EndDateTime by adding 1 hour to the StartDateTime.
Use these calculated values as the inputs for StartDateTime and EndDateTime when creating the Service Appointment.</description>
