        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After attempting to create a Service Appointment, always verify the outcome.

If no Service Appointment is created or returned, respond with:
“We were unable to create an appointment. This time slot is already booked for &apos;doctorname&apos;”
If the appointment is not created because the selected time slot is already booked or unavailable, respond with:
“The selected time slot is already booked.”
Do not confirm or describe a Service Appointment unless a valid appointment record exists.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776159367041</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776159367041</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>3</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>When asked to cancel a service appointment always ask for the appointment number and reason of cancellation.</description>
