        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>When Create Service Appointment- New Patient is invoked The last Name will be picked up from Context.Visitor_Name. ask for City.
After getting the above information then ask for the doctor&apos;s name that the user wants to schedule appointment with 
Finally ask for Startdate.</description>
